  <entry>
    <title>关于页面增加BMI检测</title>
    <link href="/hexo/2021-06/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0BMI%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B/"/>
    <url>/hexo/2021-06/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0BMI%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="任务描述"><a href="#任务描述" class="headerlink" title="任务描述"></a>任务描述</h3><ul><li>基于 fluid 主题， 在 about 页面 输入体重，自动生成 BIM 体脂率相关信息 。<h3 id="改动增加页面"><a href="#改动增加页面" class="headerlink" title="改动增加页面"></a>改动增加页面</h3></li><li>改动 hexo\source\about\index.md</li><li>新增 hexo\themes\fluid\scripts\injector.js // injector 似乎必须放在这个目录下面</li><li>新增 hexo\source\js\bmi.js <h3 id="改动逻辑"><a href="#改动逻辑" class="headerlink" title="改动逻辑"></a>改动逻辑</h3></li></ul><ol><li>about index.md   增加 页面 元素 <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html">- 1998-5 <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mark</span>&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;weight&quot;</span> &gt;</span> 40    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span>kg<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mark</span>&gt;</span> 当前 BMI :**<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;bmi&quot;</span>&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span>**    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;bmi-category&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>bmi.js 提取 index 数据 计算 并 显示 </li></ol><p><strong>计算</strong></p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">checkCategory</span>(<span class="hljs-params">value</span>) </span>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">isFinite</span>(value)) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (value &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">30.0</span>) &#123;<br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [<span class="hljs-string">`Obese`</span>];<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (value &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">25.0</span> &amp;&amp; value &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">29.9</span>) &#123;<br><br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [<span class="hljs-string">`超标了`</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>];<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (value &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">18.5</span> &amp;&amp; value &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">24.9</span>) &#123;<br><br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [<span class="hljs-string">`正常`</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;black&#x27;</span>];<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (value &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">18.4</span>) &#123;<br><br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [<span class="hljs-string">`太瘦了`</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;purple&#x27;</span>];<br>    &#125;<br>  &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">``</span>;<br>  &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>提取并展示</strong></p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> weightgroup = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementsByName(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;weight&#x27;</span>)<br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> bmigroup = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementsByName(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;bmi&quot;</span>)<br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> bmicatgroup = <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.getElementsByName(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;bmi-category&quot;</span>)<br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> height = <span class="hljs-number">175</span>;<br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> weightindex = weightgroup.length<br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> bmiMetric;<br>   <span class="hljs-comment">//console.log(weightgroup.length)</span><br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; weightindex; i++) &#123;<br>     <span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> bmi = weightgroup[i].innerHTML / (height * height); <span class="hljs-comment">// bmi in kg/cm*cm</span><br>     bmiMetric = (bmi * <span class="hljs-number">10000</span>).toFixed(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">//bmi in kg/m*m rounded to 1 decimal</span><br>     bmigroup[i].innerHTML = bmiMetric;<br>    [bmicatgroup[i].innerHTML,bmicatgroup[i].style.color]= checkCategory(bmiMetric);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>injector 注入 bmi.js 和 样式表<h3 id="效果展示"><a href="#效果展示" class="headerlink" title="效果展示"></a>效果展示</h3><a href="/about">参考</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
